{\fonttbl{\f0 Calibri;}}
\fs22
\pard\qc\b InfraMindTech Website\par
\pard\qc Structure & Technology Stack Documentation\par
\pard\qc Generated: July 10, 2026\par
\pard\par

\pard\b\fs28 1. Live URLs\par
\pard\fs22\b0
Public website: https://sudheepnbr.github.io/InfraMindTech/\par
Backend + CMS API: https://inframindtech.onrender.com/\par
Admin panel: https://inframindtech.onrender.com/admin/\par
GitHub repository: https://github.com/sudheepnbr/InfraMindTech\par
\pard\par

\pard\b\fs28 2. Architecture Overview\par
\pard\fs22\b0
- GitHub (main branch) stores the full codebase.\par
- GitHub Actions deploys frontend-only files to gh-pages branch.\par
- Render auto-deploys Flask backend, CMS admin, and content API.\par
- GitHub Pages serves the static public website.\par
\pard\par

\pard\b\fs28 3. Frontend Stack\par
\pard\fs22\b0
Markup: HTML5 (static pages)\par
CSS: Custom CSS + Bootstrap 5.3.3\par
JavaScript: Vanilla JS\par
Icons: Font Awesome 6.5.1\par
Fonts: Google Fonts (Inter)\par
Animations: AOS 2.3.4 + GSAP 3.12.5\par
Layout: Shared partials via includes.js\par
\pard\par

\pard\b\fs28 4. Backend Stack (Render Only)\par
\pard\fs22\b0
Language: Python 3.11\par
Framework: Flask 3.x\par
Server: Gunicorn\par
Config: render.yaml\par
Entry point: server.py\par
Content storage: data/content.json\par
Dependencies: flask>=3.0.0, gunicorn>=21.0.0\par
\pard\par

\pard\b\fs28 5. CMS / Admin Panel\par
\pard\fs22\b0
Admin UI: admin/index.html, admin.js, admin.css\par
Content store: data/content.json\par
Local dev: python server.py -> http://localhost:8080\par
Local admin: http://localhost:8080/admin/\par
Environment: .env (not in git)\par
\pard\par

\pard\b\fs28 6. Deployment\par
\pard\fs22\b0
GitHub Pages: .github/workflows/deploy-pages.yml -> gh-pages branch\par
Render build: pip install -r requirements.txt\par
Render start: gunicorn server:app --bind 0.0.0.0:$PORT\par
\pard\par

\pard\b\fs28 7. Website Page Structure\par
\pard\fs22\b0
Home -> /\par
Solutions -> /solutions/ (Home > Solutions)\par
Services -> /services/ (Home > Services)\par
Products -> /products/ (Home > Products)\par
Industries -> /industries/ (Home > Industries)\par
Resources -> /resources/ (Home > Resources)\par
About -> /about/ (Home > About)\par
Contact -> /contact/ (Home > Contact)\par
\pard\par

\pard\b\fs28 8. Project Folder Structure\par
\pard\fs22\b0
E:\\Website\\\par
  index.html, solutions/, services/, products/\par
  industries/, resources/, about/, contact/\par
  partials/, css/, js/, images/, data/\par
  admin/, server.py, requirements.txt, render.yaml\par
  .github/workflows/\par
\pard\par

\pard\b\fs28 9. Navigation & Branding\par
\pard\fs22\b0
- Header links go to dedicated pages with breadcrumbs.\par
- Logo: iMT icon + InfraMindTech + INNOVATE • INTEGRATE • INSPIRE\par
- Inner pages use page-header, AOS animations, page transitions.\par
- GitHub Pages loads CMS content from Render API.\par
\pard\par

\pard\b\fs28 10. Stack Summary\par
\pard\fs22\b0
Project type: Static frontend + JSON-backed CMS backend\par
Frontend: HTML / CSS / Vanilla JavaScript\par
Backend: Python Flask\par
Hosting: GitHub Pages + Render\par
Database: None (JSON file)\par
Build tools: None (no npm/Webpack)\par
Version control: Git + GitHub\par
}
